t: An Ordinance Increasing Estimated Receipts and Appropriations in the Grants Operating Other Fund, in the Amount up to $1,000,000.00, for the Purpose of Interim Funding for Disaster Assistance for COVID-19; Providing for a Severability Clause; Making This Ordinance Cumulative of Prior Ordinances; Repealing All Ordinances in Conflict Herewith; and Providing an Effective Date.
